### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### Metrics
GET http://localhost:8080/metrics

### List available slots
GET http://localhost:8080/api/slots

### First booking should succeed
POST http://localhost:8080/api/appointments/book-and-notify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "candidateId": 1,
  "slotId": 1001,
  "serviceId": 1
}

### Second booking on same slot should fail with 409 Conflict
POST http://localhost:8080/api/appointments/book-and-notify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "candidateId": 2,
  "slotId": 1001,
  "serviceId": 1
}

### View appointments after booking
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments
